<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT70">
<l>tāṉoruva ṉākit taraṇi yiṭanteṭut</l>
<l>tēṉoruva ṉāyeyiṟṟiṟ ṟāṅkiyatum yāṉoruva</l>
<l>ṉiṉṟā vaṟikiṉṟē ṉallē ṉiruṉilattaic</l>
<l>ceṉṟāṅ kaṭippaṭutta cēy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am not the only one to know today that</l>
<l>[the Lord] who became a unique Boar, dug the earth out, lifted [it] up,</l>
<l rend="indent">and bore [it] on [His] tusks</l>
<l>is the Child, [who], turning into a matchless person, went there [to Balin],</l>
<l rend="indent">and subdued the wide world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
